<%= image_tag "oak_wilt.jpg", {:width => "75", :height => "75", :alt => "Oak Wilt Larvae", :class => "left"} %>
<h2><%= link_to "Oak Wilt Vectors Emergence Thermal Model", :action => :oak_wilt %></h2>
<p>Degree-day information on emergence of insects that transmit oak wilt.</p>
</div>
<div class=", {}, fineline"></div>

